{"tid":2297186,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"2016旺角衝突3人罪成 被判監27至36個月","createTime":"2020-11-23T05:58:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-23T06:57:09.000Z","uid":240362,"like":3,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"8fc1c41704a0082b759987b089d619798d422ba6","tid":2297186,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T05:58:52.000Z","msg":"旺角衝突發生距今4年，3名男子分別被控暴動、縱火和刑事損毀等共4罪，其中首被告及第三被告王國斌早前分別承認暴動及刑毀，兩人今天（23日）在區域法院分別被判入獄36個月及27個月；而經審訊後被裁定縱火罪成的次被告，則判監36個月。<br />\n<br />\n3名被告依次是22歲酒保、32歲游泳教練和23歲學生。首被告承認於2016年2月9日，在旺角豉油街與其他人參與暴動。第三被告承認兩項刑毀罪，指他於同日在山東街與身份不詳人士，損壞屬於政府的標誌杆及行人路。次被告則否認一項縱火罪，被指用火損壞屬於中國香港體操總會的一塊橫額，早前經審訊被裁定罪成。"},{"pid":"ca96631647b90f7c251b950ceaa85da54d0fd752","tid":2297186,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:00:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b05b97704bc4af2debb9f8f1d0f38c70756dc4e","tid":2297186,"uid":281501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:01:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77f19c25fa022e8542f611cf9146e941570988a1","tid":2297186,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T06:02:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45af8fe3354c2b37b1841783b10d2586aa893c4e","tid":2297186,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":